'''般樂頓會堂'''（Bonython Hall）是[[阿德雷德|阿德雷德]]大學內的主要建築之一，位於澳洲南澳洲首府阿德雷德市中心的北平台（North Terrace）<ref name="ua1">{{cite web |url=http://nationalwinecentre.com.au/adelaidean/issues/22001/news22013.html |title=UN heritage award goes to Adelaide icon |publisher=[[University_of_Adelaide|University of Adelaide]] |accessdate=2009-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706110446/http://nationalwinecentre.com.au/adelaidean/issues/22001/news22013.html |archive-date=2011-07-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。現在該建築是澳洲的國家登記建築和南澳洲登記遺產之一<ref name="NRE">{{cite AHD|6368|Bonython Hall, North Tce, Adelaide, SA, Australia - listing on the now-defunct Register of the National Estate |date=21 March 1978|accessdate=23 August 2019}}</ref><ref name="heritage2">{{Cite AHPI |SA10878 |Bonython Hall, The University of Adelaide |accessdate=2009-03-12}}</ref>。般樂頓會堂現在主要作為阿德雷德大學各類儀式的舉辦場地使用<ref name="nws1">{{cite web |url=http://www.postcards.sa.com.au/features2008/uni_heritage_walk.html |title=University Heritage Walk: Keith takes a walk in the Adelaide City region of South Australia |work=[[Postcards_(TV_series)|Postcards SA]] |publisher=[[NWS_(TV_station)|NWS]] Nine |accessdate=2009-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110312181307/http://www.postcards.sa.com.au/features2008/uni_heritage_walk.html# |archive-date=2011-03-12 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。

